## 1. Project Context

You are working on **Suknaa (سُكنى)** — a Syrian rental platform with **TWO DISTINCT SYSTEMS**:

1. **Vacation Rentals / Holiday Homes System (بيوت العطلات / P2P)**: houses, apartments, villas, farms, cabins, chalets, studios rented as short-stay holiday homes. Modeled after Airbnb (per-listing details with room/space information). Do not describe this domain as a broad "Real Estate" marketplace in new Phase 3 work.
2. **Hospitality System (Hotels / B2B)**: hotels, hotel-apartments, resorts, hostels. Modeled after Booking.com (one establishment with multiple room types and per-unit inventory).

Bilingual (Arabic RTL + English LTR). Mohammad is the developer; he is a beginner programmer using AI tools as his primary coding partner.

