## 15. Critical v2 Reminders

1. **Two systems, never confused** — Vacation Rentals / Holiday Homes ≠ Hospitality at every layer.
2. **Commission passthrough is invisible to guest** — invoice never mentions commission.
3. **Service fee is always visible to guest** — clear line item, 2% by default.
4. **Pricing has 4 tiers** — base, weekly, monthly, seasonal overrides.
5. **Hotel inventory is per-unit** — not just a counter.
6. **Anti-circumvention requires reason** — every availability reduction logs an event.
7. **Dual reviews** — separate ratings for the stay listing (vacation rental or hotel) **and** host.
8. **Map markers are color-coded** — by category, not arbitrary.
9. **Login buttons are dual** — "as Guest" and "as Host" with same account.
10. **Tabs are persistent** — `[الكل] [بيوت العطلات] [فنادق]` on every public page (target copy; legacy UI may differ until wired).

